Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認輸了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.17,0:02:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十三話\N劍心練得飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼  小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.32,0:02:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.49,0:02:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一個人在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.52,0:02:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.66,0:02:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來陪陪我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.83,0:02:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這快死的人管我叫什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可憐的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算我們有緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.79,0:03:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救了你一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.33,0:03:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再恨再氣  他們也不會醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.63,0:03:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來吧\N免得你一個人孤伶伶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.10,0:03:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然只有你一個人存活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.94,0:03:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是值得慶幸的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼想起以前的往事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.60,0:03:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  你還要睡到幾點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.80,0:03:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.77,0:03:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再不起來  我又要回憶往事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.54,0:04:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比方說你在八歲的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.78,0:04:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還會尿床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想到你肚子餓的時候\N貪吃的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真讓人懷念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你醒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再睡一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.66,0:04:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.86,0:04:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流第十三代\N繼承者比古清十郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腕力還是一樣厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.77,0:04:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是性格還是一樣古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.97,0:04:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.94,0:04:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛脾氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.04,0:04:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤僻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.34,0:04:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我慢慢想起以前\N你的古怪脾氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.78,0:04:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是狗改不了吃屎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你這個不肖徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來就是來找我吵架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上像我這樣的老師\N已經不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.36,0:04:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廢話少說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.06,0:04:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再給你一次機會\N不然我就不教你武功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.67,0:05:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要對付老師是要靠一點頭腦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.81,0:05:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是最後的機會我要全力以赴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.84,0:05:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你  他只是個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.46,0:05:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救救他  救救這個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.20,0:06:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還要睡  快起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也未免太用力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.68,0:06:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要把我打出腦震盪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不這樣子  你也打不倒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過了十年  你還是這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.26,0:06:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵守諾言  教你武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.67,0:06:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要保持絕對的靜止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果搖動身體  你就沒命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.64,0:06:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先我先教你劍擊的基本招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唐竹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,袈裟斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逆袈裟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左切上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右切上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.19,0:06:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逆風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有刺突劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論哪一種武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.66,0:07:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是以此九種招式變化出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.26,0:07:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以說這九種招式是\N所有武功的基本結構
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.38,0:07:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流厲害之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在於能抵抗這九種招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人無法防禦招架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.09,0:07:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「九頭龍閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.56,0:07:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我最得意的武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.83,0:07:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確是讓人無法招架的招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要敵人稍有動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上予以攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.84,0:07:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是「奧義」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.44,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 在發什麼呆  快做做看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.94,0:07:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只看我做\N你怎麼可能練得會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.19,0:08:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要自己實地演練才能領悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你以前練功\N都是用這種方法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被老師拆穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你的武功一直都是半吊子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.71,0:08:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了就來攻擊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.55,0:08:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確是不能稍有動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.25,0:08:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎完全被看透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.82,0:08:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,九種招式都被掌握住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.93,0:08:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「九頭龍閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該打得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.66,0:09:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣是「九頭龍閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.33,0:09:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼差別那麼大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.13,0:09:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是我的「九頭龍閃」有問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的「九頭龍閃」沒有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.34,0:09:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是同樣的技巧\N不同的使力方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.31,0:09:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威力當然不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.78,0:09:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂擊術注重的是腕力\N突進術注重的是重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.58,0:09:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你兩者都比我差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.45,0:09:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你的九頭龍閃\N當然打不過我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.86,0:09:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是沒學會飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.90,0:10:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要打敗我的「九頭龍閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一個方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.17,0:10:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是飛天御劍流的精髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是「天翔龍閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「天翔龍閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.75,0:10:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你那個驚訝的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「九頭龍閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最得意的功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.96,0:10:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能稍有動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.80,0:10:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是最大的訣窮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.50,0:10:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「九頭龍閃」  是我最得意的武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.74,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以前沒聽人講過\N「九頭龍閃」的厲害嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被耍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.42,0:10:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實「九頭龍閃」只是教授\N飛天御劍流精髓的試驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通過「九頭龍閃」的測試後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能正式教授飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.96,0:10:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你只要能打敗我的「九頭龍閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就學會飛天御劍的精髓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想想看「九頭龍閃」的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.74,0:11:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就能聯想  「天翔龍閃」的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.14,0:11:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「九頭龍閃的樣子」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.12,0:11:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然「九頭龍閃」是無法防禦迴避的招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.59,0:11:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就只能\N利用出招前攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.13,0:11:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.66,0:11:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以換句話說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.83,0:11:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「天翔龍閃」就是超神速的武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.47,0:12:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼還不動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.84,0:12:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還在猶豫什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.54,0:12:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是你領悟的結果嗎\N真是沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.08,0:12:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道  可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.22,0:12:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.02,0:12:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怕萬一我練成了\N會傷害到老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.08,0:13:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你還沒練成功前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.45,0:13:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是沒有資格講這種話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你一個晚上的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你好好想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.02,0:13:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己要的到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.36,0:13:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你欠我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你敢以你的命償還嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有小孩來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.31,0:14:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有這麼一個小孩\N像迷路的貓兒來過這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世事難料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.23,0:14:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多事情都是自己害自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.94,0:14:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是江湖中人常會發生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.37,0:14:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本想以飛天御劍流來救人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果人沒救到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.95,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而增添許多無辜的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的隱居\N也是想向那些犧牲者謝罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還替強盜做墳墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是人口販子  不是強盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.21,0:15:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我父母去年就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是父母或是人口販子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是需要墳墓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.09,0:15:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那三個石頭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小茜、小花和小櫻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.66,0:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們三個人\N被需要錢的家人賣掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.96,0:15:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只見過他們一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.87,0:15:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是男生  反正我沒父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.94,0:15:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會誓死保護你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.91,0:15:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.31,0:15:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找不到更好的石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.08,0:15:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能找到這些  連花也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.76,0:15:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使成佛了  卻不能喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人生又有什麼意義呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點酒表示我一點心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.83,0:16:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.63,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我名字太軟弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後你就叫劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.44,0:16:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就跟著我學武功吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經十九年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.75,0:16:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許明天就是今生離別的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心什麼時候回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.03,0:16:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天就回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天你也這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天一定會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.51,0:16:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心請你快回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥  快點進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.69,0:17:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.06,0:17:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.83,0:17:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村一定會練成武功回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心只知道犧牲自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.94,0:17:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人背負那麼的重任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.98,0:17:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許學得武功\N就可以打敗志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.35,0:17:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但其實劍心的心中還是\N在殺人與不殺人之間矛盾著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.92,0:17:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.39,0:17:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天真是給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們都是關心劍心的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爺爺也會高興我這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.97,0:17:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信劍心回來時\N爺爺就會醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.17,0:17:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心一定不會背叛小薰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.54,0:17:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.71,0:17:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看我爺爺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.79,0:18:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.06,0:18:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好長的旅程\N我們比預計的時間晚到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要過一座山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,署長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前幾天抓到的張十刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.51,0:18:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來和志志雄是同一夥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.05,0:18:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相樂左之助終於到京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.05,0:19:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒領略到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.12,0:19:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.63,0:19:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你就此放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.46,0:19:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要如何超越自己\N甚至打敗志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.63,0:19:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你活著不就是為了戰勝痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.94,0:19:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打敗孤苦  維護正義嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.45,0:19:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你倒不如放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為師的最後任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.88,0:19:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是趁現在領你開悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.64,0:20:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在怕比古十清郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.11,0:20:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是怕死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我怕死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.48,0:20:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在動亂的時候\N我就沒有要活下去的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.62,0:20:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有什麼好怕死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.57,0:20:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是男生  反正我沒父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.77,0:20:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會保護你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.81,0:20:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心太  你要堅強的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.01,0:20:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還小  你不像我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以選擇自己要走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要堅強活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.99,0:20:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人生就沒有白來一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.20,0:21:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是要努力活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.45,0:21:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯  就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.09,0:21:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺手總是會一味犧牲自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.16,0:21:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.50,0:21:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以容易輕視自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.63,0:21:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺手要學會愛惜自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.94,0:21:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能保護需要被保護的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.27,0:21:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能持續守護時代的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.48,0:21:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你成功了  劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.05,0:21:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已超越自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.52,0:21:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以自己\N將「天翔龍閃」運用自如了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.82,0:22:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你決不會輸給志志雄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在你是我的徒弟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.63,0:22:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我將為師的使命傳交給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.30,0:22:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要為人民的幸福努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.04,0:22:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再為你的不殺誓言所苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.07,0:22:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而彷徨猶豫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.79,0:22:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師

